name: GATSBY
description:
Gatsby, 2D platform minigame, where you need to finish 3 levels to complete the game.

Collect fish and don't fall in the void.

Assets downloaded from the asset store, and different webpages.

Asset level 2 Parallax from https://ansimuz.itch.io/parallax-forest

Asset level 3 Parallax from https://ansimuz.itch.io/industrial-parallax-background

I'm still learning and improving everything so if you can give me some tips for that i'll be grateful.

Code https://github.com/HiBlancy/Gatsby

Currently fixing bugs and issues
